{"tid":2228140,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[自家廚房]今日唔煮飯，打邊爐","createTime":"2020-10-03T10:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T09:00:22.000Z","uid":132749,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ef6d4fe7c019f10ebc036d6670e0eebeaad28694","tid":2228140,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:27:07.000Z","msg":"尋日睇到城巴打 打邊爐，比左我女朋友睇，話好想打，今日都要打邊爐。所以就事但買左d野返黎， 當然無城巴個d咁正。 <br />\n<br />\n整左個沙嗲湯底， 買左d豬肉片，牛肉片，仲有小小菜同丸，打邊爐例排野， 但無買海鮮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FQObrZ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFQObrZ0.png&h=9f06243d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLWcVTs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLWcVTs.png&h=59667a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JaQX6Zk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJaQX6Zk.png&h=027b3d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMelbourne  lockdown 左一排今日， 自己出去都無咩野， 今日一齊出去買餸打邊爐，去Costco ， 咁就出事， 條八婆之前話要買Bruno, 係Costco 比佢見到個差唔多既爐，死都要買，今日買餐餸先幾十蚊澳紙，買個死人爐$140，真係唔去好過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係宜個咁既爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NGqxbtL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNGqxbtL.png&h=9f9e665f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 今日終於拎到我個baking stone， 黎緊會用佢拍多d麵包既片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFPJ2Bu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFPJ2Bu.png&h=61715296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n有興趣既巴絲記得subscribe 我YouTube Channel <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/channel/UCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=a0cbf905\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/channel/UCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg</a><br />\n<br />\n或者follow 我既ig <br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/openfridge_kitchendiary?igshid=tqrihvh64pc2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fopenfridge_kitchendiary%3Figshid%3Dtqrihvh64pc2&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=0fee0fbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/openfridge_kitchendiary?igshid=tqrihvh64pc2</a>"},{"pid":"9670a85faa9be5e364ba3eaf3938f8ad2b1af265","tid":2228140,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:31:29.000Z","msg":"Bieeno is jeng"},{"pid":"a281d556f34de129727292cf1da62bec6254bece","tid":2228140,"uid":132749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9670a85faa9be5e364ba3eaf3938f8ad2b1af265","tid":2228140,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:31:29.000Z","msg":"Bieeno is jeng"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:33:55.000Z","msg":"但洗野好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0108906b4b1434ac1b9f911e47269ae16a99c0c8","tid":2228140,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:34:47.000Z","msg":"你部機...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7f307dc3064b90da21d2bd59fb4a72294ed669","tid":2228140,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a281d556f34de129727292cf1da62bec6254bece","tid":2228140,"uid":132749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9670a85faa9be5e364ba3eaf3938f8ad2b1af265","tid":2228140,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:31:29.000Z","msg":"Bieeno is jeng"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10